Scroll list flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<Scroll list=>scrolllist_gadget>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0 	- Gadget can have multiple selected items when set.
	1 	- Use icons to select, rather than highlights.	(TextGadgets 0.27)
	2 	- Don't allow anything to be selected by the user.	(TextGadgets 0.27)
	3 	- Force gadget to have vertical scroll bar.	(TextGadgets 0.56)
	4	- Prevent gadget from having vertical scroll bar.	(ditto)
	5 	- Force gadget to have horizontal scroll bar.	(ditto)
	6	- Prevent gadget from having horizontal scroll bar.	(ditto)
Constants:
	<ScrollList_SingleSelections>
	<ScrollList_MultipleSelections>
	<ScrollList_IconSelection>
	<ScrollList_NoUserSelection>
	<ScrollList_VScroll_Mask>
	 	<ScrollList_VScroll_Optional>
	 	<ScrollList_VScroll_On>
	 	<ScrollList_VScroll_Off>
	 	<ScrollList_VScroll_Invalid>
	<ScrollList_HScroll_Mask>
	 	<ScrollList_HScroll_Optional>
	 	<ScrollList_HScroll_On>
	 	<ScrollList_HScroll_Off>
	 	<ScrollList_HScroll_Invalid>
#Line
#Wrap on
To be used with <ScrollList_SetState> & <ScrollList_GetState>. If the flags neither force nor prevent a scroll bar then the gadget will automatically gain one as necessary.
